snippet.title: Sonic and the Elements of Harmony [Sonic x MLP] - SAGE '21 Trailer
snippet.description:
#SonicTheHedgehog #SonicFanGames #MyLittlePony #SonicEOH 

Play as Sonic the Hedgehog and Twilight Sparkle to embark on a new adventure to stop Dr. Eggman's evil plans on taking over the magical world of Equestria.
